</section><section id="lxb_af-firm_credit-12" class="lxb_af-widget lxb_af-firm_credit lxb_af-grid-display-table_cell lxb_af-widgets-top_stripe-widget lxb_af-is_not_hamburger lxb_af-has_hamburger_sibling lxb_af-is_stuck_to_hamburger lxb_af-hamburger-position- lxb_af-text_align-right lxb_af-print_background_color-#000000 lxb_af-hide-all-gt-medium lxb_af-layout_options-lxb_af-hide-all-gt-medium"><div class='lxb_af-firm_credit-widget-logo-wrap'><a class='lxb_af-client-get_linked_logo lxb_af-client-get_linked_logo-firm_credit-widget lxb_af-client-get_linked_logo-firm_credit-widget-style-left' rel="noopener" target='_blank' href='/'><img width='220' height='57' class='lxb_af-client-get_logo' src='https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-440x114.png' alt='Law Sites logo' srcset='https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-550x143.png 550w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-120x31.png 120w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-320x83.png 320w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-768x199.png 768w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-656x170.png 656w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-40x10.png 40w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-80x21.png 80w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-160x41.png 160w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile.png 1100w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-367x95.png 367w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/title-logo-mobile-734x190.png 734w, https://www.lawsitesblog.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/509/2018/05/tit